Package: igvShiny
Title: igvShiny: a wrapper of Integrative Genomics Viewer (IGV - an interactive
    tool for visualization and exploration integrated genomic data)
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2023-11-6
Authors@R: c(
    person("Paul","Shannon", role = c("aut"), 
